               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">MR. HASLAM</hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">re-examined</hi>. I keep no cash-book of the town trade—I keep one for the country—I have only the prisoner's own handwriting as the cart list—it is my general practice to ask the prisoner if these goods are left, and he says, "Yes."</p>
